<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> X, Malcolm and Alex Haley:<i>"The Autobiography of Malcolm X"</i>, page 366. Grove Press, 1964</li>
<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> Gelderloos, Peter. <i>How Nonviolence Protects the State</i>. Boston: <a href="/wiki/South_End_Press" title="South End Press">South End Press</a>, 2007.</li>
<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> Ibid., p.7-12.</li>
